1
00:00:23,667 --> 00:00:27,571
♪The moon rests on the treetops,
listening to the evening breeze♪

2
00:00:27,616 --> 00:00:31,392
♪Wine in hand,
I sing as stars shine in disarray♪

3
00:00:31,488 --> 00:00:35,200
♪The endless night
keeps but one lonely lamp♪

4
00:00:35,456 --> 00:00:38,720
♪Who knows if I'm warm or cold♪

5
00:00:39,232 --> 00:00:43,232
♪Years of companionship
vanish like mist♪

6
00:00:43,232 --> 00:00:47,136
♪How many roads must a deep love travel♪

7
00:00:47,136 --> 00:00:50,912
♪The returned soul
wears robes of regret♪

8
00:00:51,072 --> 00:00:55,552
♪Brushing off dust with a wave♪

9
00:00:56,864 --> 00:01:00,928
♪Wind or no wind, I think of you♪

10
00:01:00,928 --> 00:01:04,600
♪Beyond words♪

11
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:10,016
♪A vow is cherished all the time♪

12
00:01:12,704 --> 00:01:16,448
♪Some souls yearn to ferment time♪

13
00:01:16,448 --> 00:01:19,800
♪Into a story♪

14
00:01:20,448 --> 00:01:23,360
♪Crushing the past,
I let old memories fade♪

15
00:01:23,744 --> 00:01:30,720
♪Don't let this story end♪

16
00:01:36,563 --> 00:01:41,824
=Beyond The Loop=

17
00:01:42,035 --> 00:01:45,248
=Episode 12=

18
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:18,560
Kerosene!

19
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,360
Help! I don't want to die!

20
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:47,168
Help! Help!

21
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:52,880
Help! Fire! There's a fire!

22
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,152
Protect the City Lord.

23
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:08,840
Wei Feng, take care
of yourself and the others.

24
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:19,680
City Lord!

25
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:48,960
Watch out!

26
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:23,080
(Tonight I will perish
in this sea of flames.)

27
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:27,520
(My Four Dreams journey may end here.)

28
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:37,800
(I never managed to change anything.)

29
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:45,400
(Wan, may you break free
from the Mu family)

30
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:49,520
(and live happily from now on.)

31
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,760
My lady.

32
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:20,640
City Lord...

33
00:05:20,840 --> 00:05:21,560
He's back?

34
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,760
Say it. What happened?

35
00:05:45,568 --> 00:05:49,680
(Spirit Tablet of Deceased Mu Yunqing)

36
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:40,480
Yunqing, my dear grandson.

37
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:46,080
Why did you leave us so soon?

38
00:06:46,784 --> 00:06:53,440
How can I face your parents now?

39
00:06:57,696 --> 00:06:59,120
Grandfather, I'll help you back.

40
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:03,640
Yunqing's spirit in heaven
wouldn't want you to be like this.

41
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,960
Please.

42
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:07,520
Let me see the City Lord one last time.

43
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:09,080
Please!

44
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:27,480
I never thought
our last farewell would be permanent.

45
00:09:21,568 --> 00:09:24,960
You didn't even shave. How unsightly.

46
00:09:27,136 --> 00:09:30,956
♪Wine in hand,
I sing as stars shine in disarray♪

47
00:09:31,136 --> 00:09:35,040
Mu Yunqing, if you're tired

48
00:09:35,104 --> 00:09:36,400
and don't want to get up,

49
00:09:37,536 --> 00:09:38,520
just sleep awhile.

50
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:40,840
I'm here.

51
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:46,520
If one day I'm no longer with you,

52
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:48,880
you must stay happy.

53
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,120
What did you say?

54
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:53,160
Because I love seeing you smile.

55
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,800
I want you to stay happy.

56
00:09:56,480 --> 00:10:00,192
♪Wind or no wind, I think of you♪

57
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:03,424
♪Beyond words♪

58
00:10:04,288 --> 00:10:06,944
♪A vow is cherished all the time♪

59
00:10:06,944 --> 00:10:09,560
♪This endless yearning♪

60
00:10:12,256 --> 00:10:14,752
♪Some souls yearn to ferment time♪

61
00:10:15,936 --> 00:10:17,680
Sparks fall into the sea.

62
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:19,640
Sun and moon lose their glow.

63
00:10:19,936 --> 00:10:23,000
Farewell, City Lord.

64
00:10:23,316 --> 00:10:27,680
♪Don't let this story end♪

65
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,160
Yunqing died.

66
00:10:40,448 --> 00:10:44,880
Jin City needs a leader.

67
00:10:46,656 --> 00:10:50,600
Our Mu family has few heirs.

68
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:55,320
Now it's only you.

69
00:11:00,416 --> 00:11:05,200
Yunhao, can you bear
this responsibility?

70
00:11:14,464 --> 00:11:18,280
Grandfather, I won't let you down.

71
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:27,000
No rush. Think it over carefully.

72
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:34,400
You failed again tonight.

73
00:11:35,872 --> 00:11:37,280
If it weren't for Mu Yunqing...

74
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:41,600
Save your excuses.

75
00:11:44,704 --> 00:11:47,880
That day you told us
to assassinate him during his wedding,

76
00:11:48,512 --> 00:11:49,920
but he was prepared,

77
00:11:50,528 --> 00:11:52,120
causing us heavy losses.

78
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:55,960
You

79
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:59,360
owe this to us.

80
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,320
Wait!

81
00:12:00,352 --> 00:12:01,000
Wait!

82
00:12:01,248 --> 00:12:02,800
I have a way to eliminate Yu Yingwan.

83
00:12:05,408 --> 00:12:06,760
You better deliver.

84
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:08,800
I will.

85
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,200
It's you.

86
00:12:24,416 --> 00:12:27,840
Fine. I'll think it over.

87
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:35,920
(I'll be the City Lord sooner or later.)

88
00:12:52,832 --> 00:12:56,704
♪Winter snow waltzes
before the courtyard♪

89
00:12:58,784 --> 00:13:02,413
♪Palaces show no mercy♪

90
00:13:03,789 --> 00:13:06,893
♪So much courage it takes♪

91
00:13:06,893 --> 00:13:09,421
♪To retrace each step♪

92
00:13:09,613 --> 00:13:14,765
♪Memory's whispers, dreams or illusion♪

93
00:13:15,917 --> 00:13:18,989
♪Butterflies climb mountains for love♪

94
00:13:18,989 --> 00:13:21,325
♪Perish before the flowers♪

95
00:13:21,837 --> 00:13:27,341
♪You seem so distant,
yet right before my eyes♪

96
00:13:27,981 --> 00:13:30,157
♪A game of chess, a fate of strife♪

97
00:13:30,157 --> 00:13:33,389
♪I dream of standing
with you, side by side♪

98
00:13:33,613 --> 00:13:35,373
♪If you would meet me face to face♪

99
00:13:35,373 --> 00:13:39,053
♪I'd die without a single regret♪

100
00:13:39,277 --> 00:13:45,101
♪You're the untouchable star♪

101
00:13:45,325 --> 00:13:51,053
♪I'm the tiniest speck♪

102
00:13:51,053 --> 00:13:54,221
♪Through all the tides of love and hate♪

103
00:13:54,221 --> 00:13:57,133
♪Our eyes met across the mortal world♪

104
00:13:57,133 --> 00:13:59,341
♪When breezes stirred by my window♪

105
00:13:59,341 --> 00:14:03,053
♪Cherry blossoms rained in the sky♪

106
00:14:03,053 --> 00:14:09,197
♪You're the distant star♪

107
00:14:09,197 --> 00:14:14,989
♪I'm the tiniest speck♪

108
00:14:15,245 --> 00:14:17,965
♪Spend all my devotion♪

109
00:14:18,381 --> 00:14:21,069
♪For your tears and embrace♪

110
00:14:21,069 --> 00:14:23,405
♪I'll brave all the blizzards♪

111
00:14:23,405 --> 00:14:27,277
♪To walk with you♪

